Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我知道在哪里  你们又打算把吠陀怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀本来就是为给我们使用而制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么告诉我  你们准备用吠陀来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚设立这个计划的真正目的又是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了即将到来的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将到来的对话？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是人类的界限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也不见得是万能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.85,0:00:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是也被我们抓住了么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是故意的话…又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 菲露特…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利塔娜小姐她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.17,0:01:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉她怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打伤了拉塞  把米蕾娜当作人质…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利塔娜小姐说自己是改革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉她？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.36,0:01:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有个什么闪失的话  人质的性命就不保了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同型号的我和亚琉的思想能相互交流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑量子波…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.47,0:01:51.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉  接下来按照预定计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内系统被…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:01:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利…利塔娜小姐  还是停下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话  大家也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.73,0:02:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想从这里过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩丽丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么知道这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为只有你们能用脑量子波
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内系统被病毒感染了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成两路去找米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐回舰桥去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死  亚琉在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩丽丝小姐来了  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把你给忘了  C level的脑量子波使用者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未完成的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切的元凶就是你们  上校的仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清英先生  斯托拉托斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  亚琉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想丢下我离开吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起走么？  能看到世界的改革哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Right  这事算我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还另外赠送Cherudim一台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来受你关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用真打吧？ 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人质被夺回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成女性的样子就这么感情用事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉要用小型艇脱离么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这系统怎么这样？ 太随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三舱门自动打开  后部舱门也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让Cherudim和OO去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借口跟利冯兹说去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam来了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂  抱歉得以夺回O-Raiser为优先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用了TRANS-AM了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备让这部机体受损么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有优秀的战术预报员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Raiser  对接模式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统被OO强行介入…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法控制…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟洛克昂说的一样  你们离万能还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  O-Raiser就放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  还是想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留点纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Raiser的输出功率…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要向我开枪么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来  亚琉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉·利塔娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪啊…瞄准开枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了什么在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么…加入卡塔隆  加入Celestial Being…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:09:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没出息的男人  莱尔·迪兰地！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的觉悟就是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔·迪兰地…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的爱你  莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你身体不适  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还是用新药比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔马克  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你抑制肆虐的体内细胞异常的药物是为了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你向我请求的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了实现没有纷争的统一世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了向Gundam报你双亲的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gun…dam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你很期待哦  这部Regnant也是特意为你带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你作为第一个成为改革者的人类  引导这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  路易丝·哈莱维
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  阿尔马克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是听话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======================================
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  舰内系统情况如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航行和战斗系统都受到了相当大的损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经清除了病毒  但被完全删除的资料达3456
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者似乎也带走了一些资料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修复要花多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最少也要2210
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  利塔娜小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就集中精神修复  敌人就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩  O-Raizer的修理情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶舱整个换掉了  但是Raizer系统的调试很花时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时是无法让OO出击的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底为什么  可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会出现在战场上的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会放过这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  你不说我也会好好干
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是改革者  是我们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是按个扳机…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么万一的话就由我来开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候你恨我也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少耍帅了  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有和她战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不和她战斗的理由更多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚  做好Seravee的出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你来操舵的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道心里没底
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你们就用Gundam来保护我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E-Senser有反应  从速度上看…应该是敌人的部队！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内系统报销了  OO也受损
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有剩下那几台Gundam的话根本不是我们的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希琳  我们的目的是虏获OO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也得让那孩子帮忙才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…兴趣真恶劣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈莱维准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是新产出的Regnant的初战  我也很期待你的战果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三台…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人数量虽少  但有MA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跟以前那台不同型号的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子光束…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然转向了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这威力！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这攻击…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被击中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里  你在哪里  亚琉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机接近  敌机接近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么激动  莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得你是个好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亚琉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是戏剧性的再会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深爱的女人是改革者  是自己的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可谓是拼上了性命的恋情啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉牵制住一台了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就看我们的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这光束！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来撕开突破口！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hyper Buster模式！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高浓度压缩粒子  开放！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hyper Buster被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios受损！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim  离开战斗宙域了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO还没调试好吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得弄上一会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  Fang！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗！ 把浮游盾设成强击模式！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们非得战斗不可！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我是改革者啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也曾心意相通！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在虚假的世界里！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说都是假的吗…不管是我的心意  还是你的感情！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干  干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你再一次…成为我的女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不会让你说「不」的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱…莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的东西就抢过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你是改革者也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不客气了！ OO！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧  亚琉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者是引导人类之人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  是位于人类之上的物种  是绝对者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被视为与人类等同  忍无可忍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让你见识一下我们之间力量的差距吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  亚琉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…我觉得自己是改革者真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是这样  就无法遇见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会在这世界上的某处擦身而过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样不好吗  那样就能活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有你的话  活着也没有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我们俩曾经心意相通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:21:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.33,0:22:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你…都是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.53,0:23:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你杀了亚琉！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.62,0:23:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想要回来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.21,0:23:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是作为改革者  而是作为人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.31,0:23:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我们身边！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.79,0:23:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明心意相通…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.65,0:23:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.74,0:23:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我也会…和路易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.81,0:23:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声响起了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.64,0:23:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.65,0:23:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的…歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生被改变之人  失去亲人之人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.72,0:24:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连锁的仇恨是否只能通过杀戮才会得报？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「革新之门」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.75,0:24:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  走向门的另一侧
